Subject: xen/arm: use dma-noncoherent.h calls for xen-swiotlb cache
 maintainance
Git-commit: 8e23c82c68635a8859820bc6feb0fb3798aed943
Patch-mainline: v5.4-rc1
References: bsc#1175713

Copy the arm64 code that uses the dma-direct/swiotlb helpers for DMA
on-coherent devices.

